This is a small map with deagle,awp and knife as weapons. If you shoot at the roof the sound "01-silverstein-your_sword_vs._my_dagger-fnt" will play once! And if you go into the teleports at t/ct spawn you will come to a area that strip your weapon and Kevlar and give u a knife after 2.5 seconds.In the knife area there is a secret button that makes tha gravity go 400. There is also a bombtarget.
